entries.title: A mailman, a NASA scientist and a park ranger: Some government employees shrug off TikTok bans
entries.description: Emmanuel Jean-Pierre is an aspiring writer who’s planning to release his first novel for young adults later this year.

entries.title: India's Gen Z grapples with Modi's dark past in clashes over new documentary
entries.description: Authorities in India have gone to extraordinary lengths to stop people from seeing a new BBC documentary that is critical of Prime Minister Narendra Modi and his role in the deadly 2002 riots in Gujarat.
